item.description:
These social gatherings are an open invitation for anyone interested in attending and/or discussing all things freedom.

RSVPs here are welcome, but there are generally at least a dozen people there even when no one responds on Meetup, so take a chance and drop on by!

Note that this meeting is now bi-weekly. Every other week there will be a meeting in Portsmouth on Thursday evening. Check the calendar for details.
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for the Seacoast Liberty meetup or look for the Seacoast Liberty table centerpiece.
item.name: NH Seacoast Liberty Dover Bi-Weekly Meetup
